OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780419953
OL,3,CIllegal vapes and cigarettes seized
OL,4,Cfrom two Hampshire shops
OL,6,FIllegal vapes, cigarettes and hand
OL,7,Frolled tobacco worth more than #3000
OL,8,Fhave been seized from two shops in
OL,9,FHampshire.
OL,11,FGeorge the sniffer dog helped trading
OL,12,Fstandards to find products concealed
OL,13,Fin an armchair and an oven in shops in
OL,14,FRingwood and Totton.
OL,16,FIt was part of a joint operation
OL,17,Fbetween Hampshire County Council's
OL,18,FTrading Standards team and Hampshire
OL,19,Fand Isle of Wight Constabulary.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
