OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780419953
OL,3,CIllegal vapes and cigarettes seized
OL,4,Cfrom two Hampshire shops
OL,6,FThe covert operation ` which took
OL,7,Fplace on Wednesday 27 May - led to the
OL,8,Fdiscovery and seizure of over 500
OL,9,Fillicit vapes, cigarettes and hand
OL,10,Frolled tobacco products across the two
OL,11,Fpremises, including products concealed
OL,12,Fon the premises in an armchair and an
OL,13,Foven.
OL,15,FThe total high street value of the
OL,16,Fseized items, had they been sold
OL,17,Fillegally, would have been #3,226.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
