PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780419953
OL,3,CIllegal vapes and cigarettes seized
OL,4,Cfrom two Hampshire shops
OL,6,FThis comes after an operation in New
OL,7,FMilton last month where Trading
OL,8,FStandards officers, supported by
OL,9,FHampshire and Isle of Wight Police and
OL,10,Fother partners, seized #8,989 worth of
OL,11,Fillicit vapes, cigarettes and rolled
OL,12,Ftobacco products.
OL,14,FCouncillor Kirsty North, Hampshire
OL,15,FCounty Council's Cabinet Lead for
OL,16,FUniversal Services, said: "This is
OL,17,Fanother impressive result in our wider
OL,18,Fcrackdown on rogue traders who put
OL,19,Fprofits before public safety.
OL,26,@xD@[OU
