OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1780419953
OL,3,CIllegal vapes and cigarettes seized
OL,4,Cfrom two Hampshire shops
OL,6,F"We are committed to working with
OL,7,FHampshire Police and our local
OL,8,Fcommunities to identify shops that
OL,9,Ftrade illegally. Dodgy traders
OL,10,Fundermine legitimate businesses and
OL,11,Frisk people's health, and this focus
OL,12,Fis paying off."
OL,14,FInformation about the sale of
OL,15,Fcounterfeit vapes or tobacco ` or any
OL,16,Fsales to underage people ` can be
OL,17,Freported in confidence to the Stop
OL,18,FIllegal Tobacco hotline on 0300 999 6
OL,19,F999 or via the website: https:/
OL,20,F/www.stop-illegal-tobacco.co.uk/
